\c 22
\s UJosiya lencwadi yomlayo
\p
\v 1 UJosiya wayeleminyaka eyisificaminwembili lapho esiba yinkosi; wabusa iminyaka engamatshumi amathathu lanye eJerusalema\x + 2 Lan. 34.1,2.\x*. Lebizo likanina lalinguJedida indodakazi kaAdaya weBhozikhathi\x + Josh. 15.39.\x*.
\v 2 Wasesenza okulungileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, wahamba ngayo yonke indlela kaDavida uyise, kaze aphambukela ngakwesokunene langakwesokhohlo\x + Dute. 5.32.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Kwasekusithi ngomnyaka wetshumi lesificaminwembili wenkosi uJosiya, inkosi yathuma uShafani indodana kaAzaliya indodana kaMeshulamu, umabhalane, endlini yeN\nd kosi\x + 2 Lan. 34.8-28.\x*\nd*, esithi:
\v 4 Yenyukela kuHilikhiya umpristi omkhulu\x + 22.8. 12.10.\x* ukuthi ahlanganise imali elethwe endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, abalindi bombundu womnyango ababeyiqoqe ebantwini\x + 12.4. 2 Lan. 34.9.\x*.
\v 5 Kabayinikele esandleni sabenzi bomsebenzi abamiswe phezu kwendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, kabayinike abenzi bomsebenzi osendlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, ukulungisa izikhala zendlu,
\v 6 kubabazi, lakubakhi, lakubabazi bamatshe, lokuthenga amapulanka lamatshe abaziweyo ukulungisa indlu.
\v 7 Kodwa akubalelwananga labo imali eyayinikelwe esandleni sabo ngoba benza ngokuthembeka\x + 12.15.\x*.
\p
\v 8 UHilikhiya umpristi omkhulu wasesithi kuShafani umabhalane: Sengifice ugwalo lomlayo endlini yeN\nd kosi\x + Dute. 31.24-26. 2 Lan. 34.14.\x*\nd*. UHilikhiya wasenika uShafani ugwalo, waselufunda.
\v 9 UShafani umabhalane wasefika enkosini, wabuyisela ilizwi enkosini wathi: Izinceku zakho seziyithulule imali eficwe endlini, zayinikela esandleni sabenzi bomsebenzi abamiswe phezu kwendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 10 UShafani umabhalane wasebika enkosini esithi: UHilikhiya umpristi unginike ugwalo. UShafani waselufunda phambi kwenkosi.
\v 11 Kwasekusithi inkosi isizwile amazwi ogwalo lomlayo, yadabula izigqoko zayo\x + 22.19. Gen. 44.13.\x*.
\v 12 Inkosi yasilaya uHilikhiya umpristi loAhikhamu indodana kaShafani loAkhibhori indodana kaMikhaya loShafani umabhalane loAsaya inceku yenkosi\x + 25.22. Jer. 26.24. 39.14. 40.5.\x*, isithi:
\v 13 Hambani liyengibuzela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni mina labantu loJuda wonke mayelana lamazwi alolugwalo oluficiweyo; ngoba yinkulu intukuthelo yeN\nd kosi\nd* esesiyibaselwe, ngoba obaba kabawalalelanga amazwi alolugwalo, ukwenza konke okubhaliweyo mayelana lathi\x + 22.17. Dute. 29.27.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Ngakho uHilikhiya umpristi loAhikhamu loAkhibhori loShafani loAsaya baya kuHulida umprofethikazi umkaShaluma indodana kaTikiva indodana kaHarihasi, umgcini wezigqoko. Wayehlala-ke eJerusalema esiGabeni seSibili. Basebekhuluma laye.
\v 15 Wasesithi kibo: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Mtsheleni lowomuntu olithume kimi:
\v 16 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Khangela, ngizakwehlisela okubi kulindawo laphezu kwabakhileyo bayo, wonke amazwi ogwalo inkosi yakoJuda elufundileyo.
\v 17 Ngenxa yokuthi bangidelile, batshisela abanye onkulunkulu impepha\x + 21.22. Dute. 29.25,26.\x*, ukuze bangithukuthelise ngawo wonke umsebenzi wezandla zabo\x + 21.6,15.\x*. Ngakho intukuthelo yami izavutha imelene lale indawo, ingacitshwa\x + 22.13.\x*.
\v 18 Kodwa enkosini yakoJuda elithumileyo ukubuza eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, lizakutsho njalo kuyo: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: \add Mayelana l\add*amazwi eliwezwileyo:
\v 19 Ngoba inhliziyo yakho ibithambile\x + Hlab. 51.17. Isa. 57.15.\x*, wazithoba phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, lapho usizwa engikukhulume ngimelene lalindawo labakhileyo bayo\x + 22.11. 1 Kho. 21.29.\x*, ukuthi bazakuba yincithakalo\x + Levi 26.31,32. 2 Lan. 29.8. 30.7. Jer. 19.8. 25.9,18. 29.18. 44.22. Mika 6.16.\x* lesiqalekiso\x + Jer. 24.9. 26.6. 44.22.\x*, wadabula izigqoko zakho, wakhala inyembezi phambi kwami, lami-ke ngizwile, kutsho iN\nd kosi\x + 22.19. Gen. 44.13.\x*\nd*.
\v 20 Ngakho, khangela, ngizakubuthela kuboyihlo, njalo uzabuthelwa engcwabeni lakho ngokuthula, lamehlo akho kawayikubona bonke ububi engizabehlisela phezu kwalindawo\x + Hlab. 37.37. Isa. 57.1,2.\x*. Basebebuyisela ilizwi enkosini.
